===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|charcole|lang=enm}}, from {{term|charren||lang=enm|to change, turn}} + {{term|cole||lang=enm|coal}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|cierran||to change, turn|lang=ang}} + {{term|col||coal|lang=ang}}, equivalent to  {{compound|char|coal}}. More at [[ajar]], [[coal]].

